a graduate of

02:09.901 --> 02:17.514
St. Edward's in Austin.

02:21.260 --> 02:29.935
I think she's now with the vice president or vice 
chancellor for agriculture, Patricia Gehring.

02:31.180 --> 02:35.546
Again, a very talented young woman. That was in the 
immediate office staff. Surrounding me, other

02:38.390 --> 02:56.316
than Bob Cherry and Clyde Freeman and Peel, was 
also on the chancellor's staff, James Bond, the

02:38.390 --> 02:56.316
attorney for the system. James had the advantage 
of knowing the of knowing the area of education

03:01.673 --> 03:07.080
quite well. He had had actually more experience 
before coming on board as attorney for the system.

03:15.550 --> 03:21.277
